oyment for themselves and also employment opportunities for others.All those youths who are possessing technical degrees from recognized institutes are eligible.All the ITI pass-outs / diploma holders in the state may also remain eligible.WB Yuvashree Arpan Scheme DetailsThe important features and highlights of WB Yuvashree Arpan Scheme are as follows:-StateWest BengalScheme TypeEmployment Generation SchemeNumber of Beneficiaries50,000 youthsAssistance AmountRs. 1 lakhAnnounced ByCM Mamata BanerjeeWB Yuvashree Arpan Scheme 2019 is expected to promote entrepreneurship of the West Bengal. Empowering entrepreneurs is going to create jobs which will led to economic growth.WB Yuvashree Arpan Scheme DetailsWB govt. has already allocated Rs. 500 crore for the project and the implementation of scheme will start from 1st April 2019. All the beneficiaries can start small and medium scale business units and the state MSME & Textile dept. is going to provide assistance.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}